---
> Rule 18 - The base questionnaire (16 questions)
> The standard questionnaire collects 16 base questions, coded Q1 to Q16. Two are conditional within the base set: Q11 is shown only when Q10 = "Regreso después de una pausa", and the Embarazo option in Q12 is shown only when Q2 = Mujer. The weight-loss optionals (Q17 to Q19) are defined in Rule 19. Question copy is production Spanish (MX); type descriptors are engineering notes. All pre-filled answers remain editable.
